{"tid":1315782,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"《BMW世紀騙案》  買過/準備買BMW新車必入","createTime":"2019-07-14T14:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T23:57:33.000Z","uid":92645,"like":4,"dislike":130,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"6da2b45ed7a25e461b3a5d740e41a4638dc16c39","tid":1315782,"uid":92645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"話今日去BMW車展睇車<br />\n睇中架320i啦，問佢幾時有新車，佢話排到下年2/3月<br />\n<br />\n心諗，我買2019年車，你下年2020年先比倒我，等成大半年你係咪玩9我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住個sales話：你想下個月8月有都得，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你加$15000要個自動開尾門功能就得</span></strong>，不過就要指定色/無得taylor made裏面啲野比你<br />\n<br />\n各位bmw車主，想問個sales係咪想水我？  有乜理由新車等成半年？ 然後有乜理由<span style=\"font-size: large;\">加錢就唔洗等？？</span>    係吾係舊車/陳列車想新車賣比我咋？"},{"pid":"ea72a451679b740a5e66f6ae41b8a69cb0573b01","tid":1315782,"uid":196924,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"每隻款佢都會入定一批喺度<br />\n你想要既色同option 有現貨咪即係俾到你囉<br />\n冇現貨咪要同原廠訂囉<br />\n有咩咁出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0a2b6c80acc2157614dbba9f3669e7f9b18c32","tid":1315782,"uid":81347,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"訂新車緊係要等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你問佢現貨有咩咪要咩點囉<br />\n8月果啲車係佢地啲現貨車 正路冇得揀option<br />\n全部一樣 除左顏色<br />\n<br />\nBenz C仔都有現貨 都係冇得揀option"},{"pid":"19d3eb0d8b976c18a15121bb32299ea66334fbee","tid":1315782,"uid":30109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"想問騙咗你乜9？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你想講佢特登唔俾你買淨車？"},{"pid":"df19e842f8f83e5f5482255131db6c5966ab67e1","tid":1315782,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"想當年上代 A仔出，都唔指排半年，冇記錯好似要一兩年"},{"pid":"1cd9a5dfb3e6b08f