moji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8107480280d088c03ae80964905c71c3f9a5e9","tid":1315782,"uid":92645,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"a05a3bfc19834c9dedde7b12eed3a53b8b480ef2","tid":1315782,"uid":231179,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6da2b45ed7a25e461b3a5d740e41a4638dc16c39","tid":1315782,"uid":92645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"話今日去BMW車展睇車<br />\n睇中架320i啦，問佢幾時有新車，佢話排到下年2/3月<br />\n<br />\n心諗，我買2019年車，你下年2020年先比倒我，等成大半年你係咪玩9我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住個sales話：你想下個月8月有都得，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你加$15000要個自動開尾門功能就得</span></strong>，不過就要指定色/無得taylor made裏面啲野比你<br />\n<br />\n各位bmw車主，想問個sales係咪想水我？  有乜理由新車等成半年？ 然後有乜理由<span style=\"font-size: large;\">加錢就唔洗等？？</span>    係吾係舊車/陳列車想新車賣比我咋？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:49:42.000Z","msg":"香港寶馬同德國訂左批車<br />\n已經生產緊/運緊黎<br />\n顏色、option 都定左<br />\n你啱嘅咪留比你<br />\n唔啱嘅就幫你落 order 排期生產<br />\n無水過你喎<br />\n不過提提你，頭批一定係德國造，第二批係咪就唔知，介意非德國造嘅最好要求係合約上寫明<br />\n<br />\n唔熟車有誤會都好正常<br />\n3系唔憂賣佣又唔係高<br />\nSales 無詳細解釋好正常<br />\n不過樓主唔好一黎就覺得全世界都諗住呃你<br />\nBMW話晒大牌子，對 sales 操守都比較著重"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"第二批吾係德國製咁大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ <br />\n第二度啲QA QC差咁多 咁呢批啲車實成日壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：買車幾大淨係買第一批（預訂）果批，遲左寧願等多一年先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a32b208215ab9c8e33954640deb3dded8723120","tid":1315782,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2eb740f2c609bd0add245e9fca517